{"tid":487622,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)第 2 3 4滴血","createTime":"2017-12-03T02:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T06:17:27.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"57a98acb31f37b708ed91f435884d17ad486f7e8","tid":487622,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:22:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=56lLbbXDiJoF0sy8PSS1jYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c37c5db2\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=56lLbbXDiJoF0sy8PSS1jYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5543102b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/89/First_blood_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F89%2FFirst_blood_ver1.jpg&h=4f09111d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.這回藍波被派返回越南調查越戰失踪軍人下落,看看他們是否已成戰俘。豈料,當藍波到達該地後,突然失去了所有的軍備器材,只剩下一把刀及一套弓箭。後來他發現了真相-他被自己的部隊出賣。在一名越南少女相助之下,藍波發揮堅強意誌及高度求生技巧,克服了一切逆境,並展開了他的複仇計畫,向出賣他的人還以顏色&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.歷經無數戰火與生死考驗，主人公，豪情勇士約翰&middot;蘭博放下手中的殺人武器，在泰國過起了平靜的修行生活。有一天，特勞特曼上校突然出現在他面前。此前不久，上校受命率部隊前往阿富汗，協助當地的聖戰勇士反抗蘇聯人的入侵。雖然在上校給的照片中，阿富汗平民飽受外敵侵略和蹂躪的情景觸目驚心，但蘭博還是拒絕了上校的邀請。某晚，特勞特曼的部隊在執行任務途中遭到蘇聯軍隊的伏擊，其本人也不幸淪為階下囚。得知這一消息，蘭博再也無法靜觀其變。浴血戰士重披戰甲，隻身闖入充滿凶險的阿富汗腹地，展開一場緊張紛呈的絕命營救&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.藍波在越戰和阿富汗戰爭之後，因為對美國生活絕望，於泰緬邊界過著與世無爭、靠捕蛇販賣為生的歸隱生活。某日總部設於科羅拉多州的泛亞洲牧師團（Pan-Asian Ministry）的一群義工來請藍波幫忙作船夫帶路，好讓義工能供給河川上游的克倫族人藥品、醫療、祈禱書及補給品。早就看穿世事的藍波以「沒有武器就沒有改變」為由拒絕，但是最終被義工莎拉&middot;米勒（Sarah Miller）說服。牧師團一行人在渡河過程中遭遇水匪，藍波為了保護莎拉不得不出手冷血的將匪徒集體擊斃，但是卻遭到了牧師團領隊麥可&middot;伯奈特（Michael Burnett）的敵視而被拒絕雇用......<br />\n<br />\n10 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=56lLbbXDiJoF0sy8PSS1jYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=26ad10be\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=56lLbbXDiJoF0sy8PSS1jYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=90946a03\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bd2710e37f539a26667d766eee128bdbf14d0a","tid":487622,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T02:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7298ed9e57f4d513db4bec1af39b3a4808092f","tid":487622,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7203d376e1e6ee864e40f886e3dfac7cd6433cb5","tid":487622,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b6f4d776300977c30615f78c98de449c7ecdc2","tid":487622,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T04:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70968c825588deab66c968248de419920155fcc","tid":487622,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a5944cf5a43103f54c9e452c6bccc8d2d0b54d","tid":487622,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}